    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to exacting standards. This specimen features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant, delivering linear boost across the rev range with no discernible shaft play. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential for unparalleled cornering precision. Every vacuum line has been meticulously inspected to ensure the complex sequential transition remains seamless. The exterior boasts factory paint with zero oxidation, while the interior preserves the driver-centric cockpit ergonomics without typical bolster wear. A rare, unmolested example for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
